C/ From PDF p. 141 of "Programming in HAL/S".  Surrounding brackets have 
C/ been removed from array variables, since they are not legal HAL/S syntax.

  VSUM:
  FUNCTION(V) VECTOR;
     DECLARE V ARRAY(*) VECTOR;
     DECLARE TOTAL VECTOR INITIAL(0);
E				    -
M    DO FOR TEMPORARY N = 1 TO SIZE(V);
E         -       -     -
M       TOTAL = TOTAL + V  ;
S  			 N:

     END;
E             -
M    RETURN TOTAL;
  CLOSE VSUM;
  